The @SK is the standard opening lead from this holding. As with the first holding on this page, this suit is headed by a 2-card sequence of touching honor cards (the @SKQ). Since this suit contains only 3 cards, however, a 2-card sequence is all that is necessary to make the highest card in the suit (the @SK) the standard opening lead.

