Lead the @C9. There are not very many deals where you should lead from a doubleton against a notrump contract, but there are occasions when you should lead from a short suit like this (for example, your partner may have bid this suit). If you do decide to lead from a doubleton against notrump, the standard opening lead is the higher of the 2 cards. |
